<p class="page" id="a2379009">[Page 9]</p>
<p>8.6 1916</p>
<p>- NOTICE -</p>
<p>Should I be so unfortunate as to get killed in action, either by bullet, Bomb, shell, hand grenade, mine, torpedo, bayonet, or Gas or any other inventions of the Devil or if I should die of any of the ills which the flesh is heir to &ndash; or more generally speaking Should I go down the Vale. and my belongings can be collected. I particularly desire and request that this book be Sent, carried or conveyed or be caused to be sent carried or conveyed to.</p>
<p>[indecipherable recipient but remainder of address reads]:</p>
<p>WARWICK<br/>QUEENSLAND. AUS]</p>
<p>Dated 18. June 1916 at Romani Canal Zone.</p>
<p>Unto thy hands O Lord I commit my soul.</p>
<p>[signature in brackets] (W Peterson)</p>
